<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَعُوذُ}</span> ... أَعْتَصِمُ، وَأَلْتَجِئُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْفَلَقِ}</span> ... الصُّبْحِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{غَاسِقٍ}</span> ... لَيْلٍ شَدِيدِ الظُّلْمَةِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِذَا وَقَبَ}</span> ... إِذَا دَخَلَ ظَلَامُهُ، وَتَغَلْغَلَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{النَّفَّاثَاتِ فِي الْعُقَدِ}</span> ... السَّاحِرَاتِ اللَّوَاتِي يَنْفُخْنَ بِلَا رِيقٍ فِي عُقَدِ الخَيْطِ؛ بِقَصْدِ السِّحْرِ، سَوَاءٌ كُنَّ نِسَاءً، أَوْ أنْفُسًا خَبِيثَةً.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَاسِدٍ}</span> ... مَنْ يَتَمَنَّى زَوَالَ النِّعْمَةِ عَنْ غَيْرِهِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>